--- skills/coordinate/PLAYBOOK.md ---
# Coordinate — playbook

The long-form reference for the coordinate skill, kept out of `SKILL.md` so the
trigger surface stays small (progressive disclosure).

## Phases

1. **Fan out.** Spawn one explorer per independent axis.
2. **Converge.** Fold every finding into the shared artifact.
3. **Gate.** Run an adversarial reviewer before shipping.
--- skills/coordinate/SKILL.md ---
# Coordinate

Drive a complex task through a team of agents. See [the playbook](PLAYBOOK.md)
for the full reference on phases, fan-out, and the reviewer gate.

## When to use

Parallel exploration across three or more independent axes, converging on a
shared artifact, with an adversarial reviewer gate before shipping.
